H(x) &amp;amp; = xH(x) + x^2H^2(x) + 1
\\
0 &amp;amp; = x^2H^2(x) + (x-1)H(x) + 1
\\
H(x) &amp;amp; = \frac{(1-x) \pm \sqrt{1-2x-3x^2}}{2x^2} 
\end{aligned}
