F_j(x) 
&amp;amp; = (x+x^2H(x))^{j-1}
\\
&amp;amp; = \left( x + \frac{1-x-\sqrt{1-2x-3x^2}}{2} \right) ^{j-1} 
\\
&amp;amp; = \left( \frac{1+x-\sqrt{1-2x-3x^2}}{2} \right)^{j-1}
\end{aligned}
